; Coverage for history.cc commodity alias in price graph

commodity EUR
    alias EURO

P 2024/01/01 EURO $1.10

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Foreign    100 EURO
    Assets:Cash

test bal -X '$'
                   0  Assets
            $-110.00    Cash
             $110.00    Foreign
--------------------
                   0
end test
